import React from "react";
import {Navbar, NavDropdown, Nav} from  "react-bootstrap";
// import axios from "axios";
import "./navbar.css";
import PaperPlane from "./paperPlane.png"

const Navi = (props) => {

  return(
  <Navbar bg="light" expand="lg">
<Navbar.Brand href=""src = {PaperPlane}></Navbar.Brand>

    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />

    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">

      <Nav className="mr-auto">
        <NavDropdown title="About" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Welcome</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Education</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Work Experience</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>

        <NavDropdown title="Projects" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Individual</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Group</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>

        <NavDropdown title="Interests" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Academic</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Art</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Other Interests</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>

        <NavDropdown title="Contact" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">My Card</NavDropdown.Item>
          <NavDropdown.Divider/>
          <NavDropdown.Item href="">Message Me</NavDropdown.Item>
        </NavDropdown>

      </Nav>

    </Navbar.Collapse>
    
        <Nav.Link href="">LinkedIn</Nav.Link>
        <Nav.Link href="">Github</Nav.Link>

  </Navbar>
  )
}

export default Navi;
